    dc:creator "Orr, Michael C.; Koch, Jonathan B.; Griswold, Terry L.; Pitts, James P." ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "Taxonomic utility of niche models in validating species concepts: A case study in Anthophora (Heliophila) (Hymenoptera: Apidae)" ;
